-- Medi-Clinic Says Hirslanden Buys Stake in Hospital for Undisclosed Amount
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-07-29T15:06:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/medi-clinic-says-hirslanden-buys-stake-in-hospital-for-undisclosed-amount.html

          
          
             Medi-Clinic Corp. Ltd. said its
Swiss business, Hirslanden, agreed to buy a 66.7 percent stake
in Klinik Stephanshorn, an 85-bed hospital in the canton of St.
Gallen, for an undisclosed amount.  
          
          


  


        